VDR Plugin 'menuorgedit' Revision History
------------------------------------------

2026-02-04: Version 0.1.0

- Initial release
- OSD-based editor for menuorg.xml
- Support for all menuorg.xml element types:
  * System menus
  * Plugins
  * Commands
  * Submenus
  * Separators
- Menu item management:
  * Add new items
  * Edit existing items
  * Delete items
  * Reorder items (move up/down)
- XML import/export functionality
- Automatic backup creation before saving
- German translation included
- Comprehensive documentation
